      "date": "2024-04-16 15:21:58.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n> Patch Set 1: Code-Review-1\n> \n> Note that patch https://review.whamcloud.com/40528 \"LU-14111 obdclass: count eviction per obd_device\" was landed in the 2.16 development cycle and seems to duplicate this patch.\n\nI agree -- that implementation is more specific and superior to mine here, so I'm going to abandon this patch.  Thanks Andreas and Aurelien!",
