        "subject": "LU-17728 obdclass: Lustre stat to track client evictions",
        "message": "LU-17728 obdclass: Lustre stat to track client evictions\n\nSupport a new stat, eviction_count, available at the root of lprocfs.\nIt is tracked and incremented by 1 for each evicted client for any\nOBD-based class.\n\nSigned-off-by: Ellis Wilson <elliswilson@microsoft.com>\nChange-Id: Ia99628b58ddab245357b4639f61a0191cf63d7f0\n"
